name: Daddy Doge
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Daddy Doge is a deflationary token that acts as a store of value on the binance smart chain. Each transaction has a unique tax that distributes tokens to holders, adds liquidity to the pool and increases funds in the marketing wallet.
